  "notes": "Northern Catalan (Rossellonès/Septentrional). Spoken in Pyrénées-Orientales, France. Eastern block. French influence: uvular rhotic [ʁ] alongside traditional [r], possible intervocalic stop voicing (French pattern), extreme final vowel deletion. Declining rapidly under French pressure.",
